# Razor View Patterns — DANGCAPNE

## File Layout

```
Views/
├── Shared/
│   ├── _Layout.cshtml      ← main layout (sidebar, navbar)
│   └── _ValidationScriptsPartial.cshtml
├── Account/
├── Home/
├── Requests/
├── HR/
├── Attendance/
└── ...
```

## ViewModel binding

```csharp
@model DANGCAPNE.ViewModels.XxxViewModel
@inject DANGCAPNE.Data.ApplicationDbContext _context
```

## Form Pattern

```html
<form asp-action="Create" method="post">
    <div class="mb-3">
        <label class="form-label">Tên nhân viên</label>
        <input asp-for="FullName" class="form-control" />
        <span asp-validation-for="FullName" class="text-danger"></span>
    </div>
    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Lưu</button>
</form>
```

## Data Table Pattern

```html
<table class="table table-hover">
    <thead>
        <tr>
            <th>STT</th>
            <th>Họ tên</th>
            <th>Phòng ban</th>
            <th>Thao tác</th>
        </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
        @foreach (var item in Model.Items)
        {
            <tr>
                <td>@(Model.Items.IndexOf(item) + 1)</td>
                <td>@item.FullName</td>
                <td>@item.Department?.Name</td>
                <td>
                    <a asp-action="Edit" asp-route-id="@item.Id" class="btn btn-sm btn-secondary">
                        <i class="bi bi-pencil"></i>
                    </a>
                </td>
            </tr>
        }
    </tbody>
</table>
```

